data.description: Nestled in the exclusive Balmoral Gated Community, this beautiful home offers over 3000 square feet of space, and has 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths!  Balmoral in Humble offers residents a world class crystal lagoon, zero entry pool, surrounded by white sand beaches and cabanas, volleyball courts, parks, an infinity pool, splash pad, recreation center, golf, and walking trails. This well cared for home boasts modern fixtures, a thoughtfully designed floor plan, and a dream kitchen.  The seller has just put in new carpet upstairs and painted the interior common areas. Not to be overlooked is the stunning master suite with huge closet and bathroom.  Great location as well, off Beltway 8 and Highway 59, commuters enjoy easy access to George Bush Intercontinental Airport and Downtown Houston. Walking distance to Ridge Creek Elementary.  Schedule your showing today!
